```{r pancreas 32266574, include=FALSE}

PMID_32266574 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32266574', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32266574 <- paste0(PMID_32266574$journal,' ', PMID_32266574$year, ' ', PMID_32266574$month,';', PMID_32266574$volume,'(', PMID_32266574$number,'):', PMID_32266574$pages)

PubMed_32266574 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32266574$eprint)

doi_32266574 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32266574$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)
```
